        Traverses the hierarchy depth-first, starting in the specified element.
        Parameters:
        hierarchy - Hierarchy to visit.
        visitor - Visitor.
        element - Starting element. If null the call is equivalent to visitDepthFirst(visitor).
        includeStarting - Whether to include the starting element.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the specified element is not part of the hierarchy.
